profile:
Professional, precise, perfect installation every time. Your satisfaction and peace of mind is our only goal.

We know your time is valuable so we always strive to be sensitive to the constraints of your busy schedule. Same day service is generally very doable, as well as evenings and weekends. 

We aim to offer the most premier design, installation and assembly services in the Toronto, GTA and surrounding areas. We work closely with all our clients to make sure every project is completed to our exacting standards. We will not rest until you are fully satisfied and thrilled with the final results.

So whether you need a kitchen designed and installed or house full of furniture put together or an organization solution figured out we have you covered. Or maybe you want to know what would be the best types of curtains or blinds to put in your house or condo? Let us advise you. If you want to make the most efficient use of your space we know what furniture makes the most sense. These services and more are what we wish to facilitate for youâ¦

We can handle any project â large or small. Give us a call, text or email and we will be happy to resolve any questions you may have!

With our 25 years of combined installation experience and knowledge you can rest assured that your job will be done to the highest standards in our industry.

profile: Founded in 2000, sohoConcept has been serving its trusting customers with a sustainable and innovative design approach, while maintaining distribution points in New York and Toronto. Our collection includes a range of contemporary furniture suitable for contract or residential projects of any size. Each piece of furniture, bearing the sohoConcept name, is born from a focus on the essentials: long-term durability and high quality translated into a clean-lined form language. Our comprehensive furnishing systems are designed to fit in a myriad of situations ranging from public spaces to offices, as well as homes. This business model grants sohoConcept cutting edge competitiveness in quality and value and consequently promotes customer satisfaction. Additionally, sohoConcept is committed to provide both fashion and comfort, while managing a high stock system with reasonable pricing. Our exclusive furniture collection is displayed in our showroom in Manhattan, NYC.
